verses.text_plain: Praise ye the Lord. Praise, O ye servants of the Lord, praise the name of the Lord.
verses.verse_html:
1Praise ye the Lord. Praise, O ye servants of the Lord, praise the name of the Lord. ▼
▼ Praise ye…: Heb. Hallelujah

footnotes.body_html: ▼ Praise ye…: Heb. Hallelujah

verses.text_plain: Blessed be the name of the Lord from this time forth and for evermore.
verses.verse_html: 2Blessed be the name of the Lord from this time forth and for evermore.

verses.text_plain: From the rising of the sun unto the going down of the same the Lord’s name is to be praised.
verses.verse_html: 3From the rising of the sun unto the going down of the same the Lord’s name is to be praised.

verses.text_plain: The Lord is high above all nations, and his glory above the heavens.
verses.verse_html: 4The Lord is high above all nations, and his glory above the heavens.

verses.text_plain: Who is like unto the Lord our God, who dwelleth on high,
verses.verse_html:
5Who is like unto the Lord our God, who dwelleth on high, ▼
▼ dwelleth…: Heb. exalteth himself to dwell

footnotes.body_text: ▼ dwelleth…: Heb. exalteth himself to dwell
footnotes.body_html: ▼ dwelleth…: Heb. exalteth himself to dwell

verses.text_plain: Who humbleth himself to behold the things that are in heaven, and in the earth!
verses.verse_html: 6Who humbleth himself to behold the things that are in heaven, and in the earth!

verses.text_plain: He raiseth up the poor out of the dust, and lifteth the needy out of the dunghill;
verses.verse_html: 7He raiseth up the poor out of the dust, and lifteth the needy out of the dunghill;

verses.text_plain: That he may set him with princes, even with the princes of his people.
verses.verse_html: 8That he may set him with princes, even with the princes of his people.

verses.text_plain: He maketh the barren woman to keep house, and to be a joyful mother of children. Praise ye the Lord.
verses.verse_html:
9He maketh the barren woman to keep house, and to be a joyful mother of children. Praise ye the Lord. ▼
▼ to keep…: Heb. to dwell in an house

footnotes.body_text: ▼ to keep…: Heb. to dwell in an house
footnotes.body_html: ▼ to keep…: Heb. to dwell in an house
